description:
Add method to internal/ticks/client.go to set verdict and trigger processing:

```go
func (c *Client) SetVerdict(taskID string, verdict string, feedback string) error {
    // Add feedback note first (if provided) to avoid race condition
    if feedback != "" {
        if err := c.AddNote(taskID, feedback, "--from", "human"); err != nil {
            return err
        }
    }

    // Set verdict - this triggers processing in tk CLI
    return c.runCommand("update", taskID, "--verdict", verdict)
}
```

Acceptance criteria:
- [ ] SetVerdict method implemented
- [ ] Feedback note added BEFORE verdict (atomic operation)
- [ ] Uses --from human flag for feedback notes
- [ ] Errors handled appropriately
